.opencode/skills/sk-doc/shared/scripts/frontmatter-version.mjs:3:// COMPONENT: Frontmatter Versioning Engine
.opencode/skills/sk-doc/shared/scripts/frontmatter-version.mjs-4-// ───────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
.opencode/skills/sk-doc/shared/scripts/frontmatter-version.mjs-5-// Deterministic compute / insert / verify of the 4-part `version`
.opencode/skills/sk-doc/shared/scripts/frontmatter-version.mjs:6:// frontmatter field for in-scope skill docs.
.opencode/skills/sk-doc/shared/scripts/frontmatter-version.mjs-7-//
.opencode/skills/sk-doc/shared/scripts/frontmatter-version.mjs:8:// Standard: .opencode/skills/sk-doc/shared/references/frontmatter-versioning.md
.opencode/skills/sk-doc/shared/scripts/frontmatter-version.mjs-9-//
.opencode/skills/sk-doc/shared/scripts/frontmatter-version.mjs-10-// Usage:
.opencode/skills/sk-doc/shared/scripts/frontmatter-version.mjs:11://   node frontmatter-version.mjs compute [--skill <name>] [--manifest-out <path>]
.opencode/skills/sk-doc/shared/scripts/frontmatter-version.mjs:12://   node frontmatter-version.mjs apply   [--skill <name>] [--paths <file>] [--update]
.opencode/skills/sk-doc/shared/scripts/frontmatter-version.mjs:13://   node frontmatter-version.mjs verify  [--skill <name>] [--paths <file>]
.opencode/skills/sk-doc/shared/scripts/frontmatter-version.mjs-14-//
.opencode/skills/sk-doc/shared/scripts/frontmatter-version.mjs-15-// compute  : dry-run; writes nothing. Emits a CSV + JSON manifest and a summary.
.opencode/skills/sk-doc/shared/scripts/frontmatter-version.mjs-16-// apply    : inserts/updates `version` per the idempotency rules.
.opencode/skills/sk-doc/shared/scripts/frontmatter-version.mjs:17:// verify   : checks every in-scope file's version == computed and frontmatter is intact.
.opencode/skills/sk-doc/shared/scripts/frontmatter-version.mjs-18-//
.opencode/skills/sk-doc/shared/scripts/frontmatter-version.mjs-19-// Determinism: same git state + same selection => identical manifest and identical bytes.
.opencode/skills/sk-doc/shared/scripts/frontmatter-version.mjs-20-// ───────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
--
