.opencode/skills/sk-doc/create-manual-testing-playbook/assets/manual-testing-playbook-template.md-1----
.opencode/skills/sk-doc/create-manual-testing-playbook/assets/manual-testing-playbook-template.md-2-title: Manual Testing Playbook Creation - Templates and Standards
.opencode/skills/sk-doc/create-manual-testing-playbook/assets/manual-testing-playbook-template.md:3:description: Templates for creating feature-catalog-style manual testing playbooks with an integrated root playbook, root-level per-feature files, current frontmatter conventions, and orchestration guidance.
.opencode/skills/sk-doc/create-manual-testing-playbook/assets/manual-testing-playbook-template.md-4-trigger_phrases:
.opencode/skills/sk-doc/create-manual-testing-playbook/assets/manual-testing-playbook-template.md-5-  - "manual testing playbook template"
.opencode/skills/sk-doc/create-manual-testing-playbook/assets/manual-testing-playbook-template.md-6-  - "testing playbook scaffold"
--
.opencode/skills/sk-doc/create-manual-testing-playbook/assets/manual-testing-playbook-template.md-13-
.opencode/skills/sk-doc/create-manual-testing-playbook/assets/manual-testing-playbook-template.md-14-# Manual Testing Playbook Creation - Templates and Standards
.opencode/skills/sk-doc/create-manual-testing-playbook/assets/manual-testing-playbook-template.md-15-
.opencode/skills/sk-doc/create-manual-testing-playbook/assets/manual-testing-playbook-template.md:16:Templates for creating manual testing playbooks with deterministic scenarios, structured evidence collection, integrated root-level review/orchestration guidance, root-level per-feature files, and current frontmatter conventions.
.opencode/skills/sk-doc/create-manual-testing-playbook/assets/manual-testing-playbook-template.md-17-
.opencode/skills/sk-doc/create-manual-testing-playbook/assets/manual-testing-playbook-template.md-18----
.opencode/skills/sk-doc/create-manual-testing-playbook/assets/manual-testing-playbook-template.md-19-
--
.opencode/skills/sk-doc/create-manual-testing-playbook/assets/manual-testing-playbook-template.md-24-**Key Characteristics**:
.opencode/skills/sk-doc/create-manual-testing-playbook/assets/manual-testing-playbook-template.md-25-- **Deterministic**: Every scenario has an exact prompt and exact command sequence.
.opencode/skills/sk-doc/create-manual-testing-playbook/assets/manual-testing-playbook-template.md-26-- **9-column contract**: Standardized table covering Feature ID through Failure Triage.
.opencode/skills/sk-doc/create-manual-testing-playbook/assets/manual-testing-playbook-template.md:27:- **Feature-catalog rooted**: The root playbook acts as the directory, review surface, and cross-reference index.
.opencode/skills/sk-doc/create-manual-testing-playbook/assets/manual-testing-playbook-template.md-28-- **Per-feature files**: Each scenario gets its own file in a category folder at the playbook root.
.opencode/skills/sk-doc/create-manual-testing-playbook/assets/manual-testing-playbook-template.md-29-- **Orchestrator-led**: Scenarios should mimic real user testing, including coordinator prompts, delegation decisions, and user-visible outcomes.
.opencode/skills/sk-doc/create-manual-testing-playbook/assets/manual-testing-playbook-template.md-30-- **Integrated root guidance**: Review protocol and orchestration rules live inside the root playbook, not in separate canonical sidecar docs.
.opencode/skills/sk-doc/create-manual-testing-playbook/assets/manual-testing-playbook-template.md:31:- **Feature-catalog shaped files**: Per-feature playbook files should mirror feature-catalog snippet structure by leading with prose, then current reality, then structured source references.
.opencode/skills/sk-doc/create-manual-testing-playbook/assets/manual-testing-playbook-template.md-32-- **Evidence-driven**: Every scenario requires captured evidence with explicit verdicts.
.opencode/skills/sk-doc/create-manual-testing-playbook/assets/manual-testing-playbook-template.md:33:- **Validator-limited**: The current validator checks the root playbook for markdown structure, but it does not recurse into category folders or verify cross-file references yet.
.opencode/skills/sk-doc/create-manual-testing-playbook/assets/manual-testing-playbook-template.md:34:- **Evergreen**: Playbooks validate current behavior. Scenario IDs are allowed; spec or phase packet-history references are not.
.opencode/skills/sk-doc/create-manual-testing-playbook/assets/manual-testing-playbook-template.md-35-
.opencode/skills/sk-doc/create-manual-testing-playbook/assets/manual-testing-playbook-template.md:36:**Location Convention**: `{SKILL_PATH}/manual-testing-playbook/`
.opencode/skills/sk-doc/create-manual-testing-playbook/assets/manual-testing-playbook-template.md-37-
