.opencode/skills/sk-doc/create-manual-testing-playbook/README.md:1:# create-manual-testing-playbook
.opencode/skills/sk-doc/create-manual-testing-playbook/README.md-2-
.opencode/skills/sk-doc/create-manual-testing-playbook/README.md-3-Author reusable manual testing playbook packages with deterministic scenarios, evidence capture, release-readiness review, and multi-operator or multi-agent execution planning.
.opencode/skills/sk-doc/create-manual-testing-playbook/README.md-4-
.opencode/skills/sk-doc/create-manual-testing-playbook/README.md-5-## 1. OVERVIEW
.opencode/skills/sk-doc/create-manual-testing-playbook/README.md-6-
.opencode/skills/sk-doc/create-manual-testing-playbook/README.md:7:This workflow packet turns a request for operator-facing validation into a `manual-testing-playbook/` package: one root playbook holding shared policy and review protocol, plus one file per feature scenario holding the exact prompt, commands, expected signals, evidence, and pass/fail criteria. It keeps every scenario deterministic enough for another operator or agent to reproduce the verdict, rather than leaving validation as an ad hoc checklist.
.opencode/skills/sk-doc/create-manual-testing-playbook/README.md-8-
.opencode/skills/sk-doc/create-manual-testing-playbook/README.md-9-## 2. WHEN TO USE
.opencode/skills/sk-doc/create-manual-testing-playbook/README.md-10-
--
.opencode/skills/sk-doc/create-manual-testing-playbook/README.md-12-
.opencode/skills/sk-doc/create-manual-testing-playbook/README.md-13-Good fits:
.opencode/skills/sk-doc/create-manual-testing-playbook/README.md-14-
.opencode/skills/sk-doc/create-manual-testing-playbook/README.md:15:- `/create:manual-testing-playbook`
.opencode/skills/sk-doc/create-manual-testing-playbook/README.md:16:- Creating `manual-testing-playbook/manual-testing-playbook.md`
.opencode/skills/sk-doc/create-manual-testing-playbook/README.md-17-- Building one file per feature scenario
.opencode/skills/sk-doc/create-manual-testing-playbook/README.md-18-- Defining exact prompts, commands, expected signals, evidence, pass/fail criteria, and failure triage
.opencode/skills/sk-doc/create-manual-testing-playbook/README.md-19-- Planning validation across humans, agents, CLIs, MCP tools, or runtime surfaces
.opencode/skills/sk-doc/create-manual-testing-playbook/README.md-20-- Converting an ad hoc release checklist into a reusable evidence-driven playbook
.opencode/skills/sk-doc/create-manual-testing-playbook/README.md-21-- Aligning manual scenarios with a feature catalog
.opencode/skills/sk-doc/create-manual-testing-playbook/README.md-22-
.opencode/skills/sk-doc/create-manual-testing-playbook/README.md:23:Skip it when a small feature only needs checklist rows in a spec folder, automated tests cover the only meaningful criteria, or the user asked for generic markdown cleanup instead of a playbook package.
.opencode/skills/sk-doc/create-manual-testing-playbook/README.md-24-
.opencode/skills/sk-doc/create-manual-testing-playbook/README.md-25-## 3. WHAT'S INSIDE
.opencode/skills/sk-doc/create-manual-testing-playbook/README.md-26-
.opencode/skills/sk-doc/create-manual-testing-playbook/README.md-27-- `SKILL.md`: Authoritative packet contract, activation rules, package shape, workflow, validation expectations, and hard rules.
.opencode/skills/sk-doc/create-manual-testing-playbook/README.md-28-- `references/README.md`: Reference map routing to the overflow detail - prompt voice (`prompt-voice.md`), common pitfalls (`common-pitfalls.md`), and reference implementations (`examples.md`). The complete workflow lives in `SKILL.md`.
.opencode/skills/sk-doc/create-manual-testing-playbook/README.md:29:- `assets/manual-testing-playbook-template.md`: Source scaffold for `manual-testing-playbook/manual-testing-playbook.md`.
.opencode/skills/sk-doc/create-manual-testing-playbook/README.md:30:- `assets/manual-testing-playbook-snippet-template.md`: Source scaffold for `manual-testing-playbook/{CATEGORY_DIR}/{FEATURE_SLUG}.md`; both placeholder values must be kebab-case.
.opencode/skills/sk-doc/create-manual-testing-playbook/README.md-31-- `changelog/.gitkeep`: Reserved changelog directory placeholder.
.opencode/skills/sk-doc/create-manual-testing-playbook/README.md-32-- No packet-local `scripts/` directory currently exists.
.opencode/skills/sk-doc/create-manual-testing-playbook/README.md:33:- Shared validators live under `../shared/scripts/`, including `validate_document.py` and `extract_structure.py`.
.opencode/skills/sk-doc/create-manual-testing-playbook/README.md-34-
.opencode/skills/sk-doc/create-manual-testing-playbook/README.md-35-## 4. CANONICAL OUTPUT SHAPE
.opencode/skills/sk-doc/create-manual-testing-playbook/README.md-36-
.opencode/skills/sk-doc/create-manual-testing-playbook/README.md-37-```text
.opencode/skills/sk-doc/create-manual-testing-playbook/README.md:38:manual-testing-playbook/
.opencode/skills/sk-doc/create-manual-testing-playbook/README.md:39:├── manual-testing-playbook.md
.opencode/skills/sk-doc/create-manual-testing-playbook/README.md-40-├── category-name/
.opencode/skills/sk-doc/create-manual-testing-playbook/README.md-41-│   ├── feature-name.md
