--
.opencode/skills/sk-doc/create-manual-testing-playbook/README.md-52-
.opencode/skills/sk-doc/create-manual-testing-playbook/README.md-53-1. Read `SKILL.md`.
.opencode/skills/sk-doc/create-manual-testing-playbook/README.md-54-2. Skim `references/README.md` for overflow detail (prompt voice, pitfalls, examples) as needed.
.opencode/skills/sk-doc/create-manual-testing-playbook/README.md:55:3. Copy the root scaffold from `assets/manual-testing-playbook-template.md`.
.opencode/skills/sk-doc/create-manual-testing-playbook/README.md:56:4. Create `manual-testing-playbook/manual-testing-playbook.md`.
.opencode/skills/sk-doc/create-manual-testing-playbook/README.md:57:5. Define category folders using a descriptive kebab-case slug such as `category-name`; the root `manual-testing-playbook.md` owns display order, not the folder name.
.opencode/skills/sk-doc/create-manual-testing-playbook/README.md:58:6. Create one per-feature file per feature ID from `assets/manual-testing-playbook-snippet-template.md`.
.opencode/skills/sk-doc/create-manual-testing-playbook/README.md-59-7. Keep prompt fields synchronized between the root summary, `SCENARIO CONTRACT`, and execution table.
.opencode/skills/sk-doc/create-manual-testing-playbook/README.md:60:8. Validate the root playbook from the repo root (replace `<SKILL_PATH>` with the target skill directory, e.g. `.opencode/skills/system-spec-kit`):
.opencode/skills/sk-doc/create-manual-testing-playbook/README.md-61-
.opencode/skills/sk-doc/create-manual-testing-playbook/README.md-62-```bash
.opencode/skills/sk-doc/create-manual-testing-playbook/README.md:63:python3 .opencode/skills/sk-doc/shared/scripts/validate_document.py <SKILL_PATH>/manual-testing-playbook/manual-testing-playbook.md --type reference
.opencode/skills/sk-doc/create-manual-testing-playbook/README.md:64:python3 .opencode/skills/sk-doc/shared/scripts/extract_structure.py <SKILL_PATH>/manual-testing-playbook/manual-testing-playbook.md
.opencode/skills/sk-doc/create-manual-testing-playbook/README.md-65-```
.opencode/skills/sk-doc/create-manual-testing-playbook/README.md-66-
.opencode/skills/sk-doc/create-manual-testing-playbook/README.md:67:Then manually spot-check per-feature frontmatter, numbered sections, divider lines, feature ID counts, prompt synchronization, and local links.
.opencode/skills/sk-doc/create-manual-testing-playbook/README.md-68-
.opencode/skills/sk-doc/create-manual-testing-playbook/README.md:69:The source templates retain their current underscore filenames until their separate source-file migration. Those source names are not emitted package names.
.opencode/skills/sk-doc/create-manual-testing-playbook/README.md-70-
.opencode/skills/sk-doc/create-manual-testing-playbook/README.md-71-## 6. HUB RELATIONSHIP
.opencode/skills/sk-doc/create-manual-testing-playbook/README.md-72-
