.opencode/skills/sk-doc/create-manual-testing-playbook/references/prompt-voice.md-40-| Code review on a PR, commit/git workflows, bug fixes, code questions, preference questions. | Safety-refusal scenarios where role context determines behavior (e.g., "git safety reviewer" decides whether to refuse a `--no-verify`). |
