.opencode/skills/sk-doc/create-manual-testing-playbook/references/common-pitfalls.md-35-| Unsynced prompt fields | Operators do not know which prompt is canonical | Update `SCENARIO CONTRACT`, the table prompt, and the root summary together |
.opencode/skills/sk-doc/create-manual-testing-playbook/references/common-pitfalls.md:36:| Broken feature-catalog links | Scenario traceability is lost | Link each scenario to its catalog entry or clearly document the exception |
.opencode/skills/sk-doc/create-manual-testing-playbook/references/common-pitfalls.md-37-| Bare command paraphrase prompts | Fails realistic orchestrator-led testing | Rewrite prompts around user intent, evidence, and verdict |
.opencode/skills/sk-doc/create-manual-testing-playbook/references/common-pitfalls.md-38-| Overloading root summaries with full execution detail | Root doc becomes noisy and hard to review | Keep full execution truth in the per-feature file |
.opencode/skills/sk-doc/create-manual-testing-playbook/references/common-pitfalls.md-39-
