.opencode/skills/sk-doc/create-manual-testing-playbook/changelog/v1.0.0.0.md-8-**Released:** 2026-07-06
.opencode/skills/sk-doc/create-manual-testing-playbook/changelog/v1.0.0.0.md-9-
.opencode/skills/sk-doc/create-manual-testing-playbook/changelog/v1.0.0.0.md:10:Initial release of `create-manual-testing-playbook`, one of the ten workflow packets in the `sk-doc` parent hub's workflow-only architecture. It authors `manual-testing-playbook/` packages: a root `manual_testing_playbook.md` plus numbered `NN--category-name` folders of per-feature files, each carrying a deterministic scenario contract (exact prompt, exact command sequence, expected signals, evidence, pass/fail criteria, failure triage) so another operator or agent can reproduce the verdict.
.opencode/skills/sk-doc/create-manual-testing-playbook/changelog/v1.0.0.0.md-11-
.opencode/skills/sk-doc/create-manual-testing-playbook/changelog/v1.0.0.0.md-12-## What's Included
.opencode/skills/sk-doc/create-manual-testing-playbook/changelog/v1.0.0.0.md-13-
.opencode/skills/sk-doc/create-manual-testing-playbook/changelog/v1.0.0.0.md-14-- `SKILL.md` -- the packet contract: activation triggers and non-triggers, the canonical package shape (root playbook plus category folders and per-feature files), the 18-step authoring workflow, scenario design rules (determinism, natural-human vs RCAF prompt voice, the prompt synchronization gate), and the validation/release gates.
.opencode/skills/sk-doc/create-manual-testing-playbook/changelog/v1.0.0.0.md-15-- `references/manual_testing_playbook_creation.md` -- standards and rationale for package structure, root-vs-per-feature responsibilities, prompt quality, and validation.
.opencode/skills/sk-doc/create-manual-testing-playbook/changelog/v1.0.0.0.md:16:- `assets/testing_playbook/manual-testing-playbook-template.md` -- root playbook scaffold.
.opencode/skills/sk-doc/create-manual-testing-playbook/changelog/v1.0.0.0.md:17:- `assets/testing_playbook/manual-testing-playbook-snippet-template.md` -- per-feature scenario scaffold.
.opencode/skills/sk-doc/create-manual-testing-playbook/changelog/v1.0.0.0.md-18-
.opencode/skills/sk-doc/create-manual-testing-playbook/changelog/v1.0.0.0.md-19-## Notes
.opencode/skills/sk-doc/create-manual-testing-playbook/changelog/v1.0.0.0.md-20-
.opencode/skills/sk-doc/create-manual-testing-playbook/changelog/v1.0.0.0.md:21:This packet has no packet-local `scripts/`; validation runs through the shared `../shared/scripts/validate_document.py` and `extract_structure.py`. It also carries no packet-local `graph-metadata.json` -- the single advisor identity and mode registry live at the `sk-doc` hub root.
--
