.opencode/skills/sk-doc/create-feature-catalog/changelog/v1.0.0.0.md-7-
.opencode/skills/sk-doc/create-feature-catalog/changelog/v1.0.0.0.md:8:Initial release of `create-feature-catalog`, one of the ten workflow packets in the `sk-doc` parent hub's workflow-only architecture. The packet authors canonical feature-inventory packages: a root `feature-catalog/feature-catalog.md` catalog organized into numbered category folders, with one source-anchored per-feature file per root entry, so a system's shipped behavior has a single reviewable current-state reference.
