.opencode/skills/sk-doc/create-feature-catalog/changelog/v1.0.0.0.md-12-- `SKILL.md` — the packet's inline workflow contract: when to create a catalog versus keep a README summary, the canonical package shape (`feature_catalog.md` + `NN--category-name/` folders + per-feature files), the 14-step creation workflow, root-catalog and per-feature-file content requirements, the catalog/playbook boundary, and the ALWAYS/NEVER/ESCALATE rules.
.opencode/skills/sk-doc/create-feature-catalog/changelog/v1.0.0.0.md-13-- `references/feature_catalog_creation.md` — the deep-dive creation reference for overflow guidance beyond the inline workflow.
.opencode/skills/sk-doc/create-feature-catalog/changelog/v1.0.0.0.md:14:- `assets/feature-catalog/feature-catalog-template.md` — the scaffold for the root `feature-catalog/feature-catalog.md`.
