.opencode/skills/sk-doc/create-feature-catalog/changelog/v1.0.0.0.md-16-
.opencode/skills/sk-doc/create-feature-catalog/changelog/v1.0.0.0.md-17-This packet has no packet-local `scripts/` or `graph-metadata.json`; validation and advisor identity are consumed from the shared `sk-doc` backbone.
