.opencode/skills/sk-doc/create-benchmark/SKILL.md:226:Before writing any benchmark folder, run label, fixture, profile, or authored report name, validate the resolved artifact path or slug with the shared checker. Router family keys such as `model_benchmark` are identifiers and are not passed as filesystem names.
.opencode/skills/sk-doc/create-benchmark/SKILL.md-227-
.opencode/skills/sk-doc/create-benchmark/SKILL.md-228-```bash
.opencode/skills/sk-doc/create-benchmark/SKILL.md:229:python3 .opencode/skills/sk-doc/shared/scripts/check_authored_name_kebab.py <artifact-path-or-slug>
