.opencode/skills/sk-doc/create-benchmark/SKILL.md-561-- Each fixture parses as JSON, carries its family's field set, and its `id` matches every profile that references it.
.opencode/skills/sk-doc/create-benchmark/SKILL.md-562-- Each code-task oracle's `expect` values come from a verified reference implementation, with held-out `hidden_tests[]`.
.opencode/skills/sk-doc/create-benchmark/SKILL.md:563:- Each profile names a scorer matching every fixture shape it scores and expands the `{spec_folder}` token in `outputsDir` rather than hard-coding a path.
.opencode/skills/sk-doc/create-benchmark/SKILL.md-564-- No evaluator, scorer, or reviewer-verdict contract was copied here; each is cross-linked to its deep-improvement authority.
.opencode/skills/sk-doc/create-benchmark/SKILL.md:565:- The authored `.md` templates and guide validate with the shared sk-doc validator, and the shipped `.json` parses.
