.opencode/skills/sk-doc/create-benchmark/SKILL.md-593-evidence pointers, then stop. Never invoke the peer adapter or deep-alignment from
.opencode/skills/sk-doc/create-benchmark/SKILL.md-594-this authoring branch. Adapter implementation, S-dimension and severity semantics,
.opencode/skills/sk-doc/create-benchmark/SKILL.md-595-discovery, convergence, reduction, and generated reports stay lane-owned.
