.opencode/skills/sk-doc/create-manual-testing-playbook/SKILL.md-28-- Planning manual validation across multiple operators, agents, CLIs, MCP tools, or runtime surfaces.
.opencode/skills/sk-doc/create-manual-testing-playbook/SKILL.md-29-- Converting an ad hoc release checklist into a reusable evidence-driven playbook package.
