.opencode/skills/sk-doc/create-feature-catalog/SKILL.md-28-- Creating a canonical feature inventory for a skill, system, MCP surface, CLI surface, or documentation family.
.opencode/skills/sk-doc/create-feature-catalog/SKILL.md:29:- Splitting a large feature surface into a root catalog plus per-feature files.
.opencode/skills/sk-doc/create-feature-catalog/SKILL.md-30-- Documenting shipped behavior with source-file anchors, validation anchors, and stable feature slugs.
.opencode/skills/sk-doc/create-feature-catalog/SKILL.md:31:- Creating or updating `feature-catalog/feature-catalog.md`.
.opencode/skills/sk-doc/create-feature-catalog/SKILL.md-32-- Creating category folders such as `retrieval/` or `mutation/`.
.opencode/skills/sk-doc/create-feature-catalog/SKILL.md-33-- Creating per-feature files such as `unified-context-retrieval.md` under category folders.
.opencode/skills/sk-doc/create-feature-catalog/SKILL.md-34-- Linking manual testing playbooks, README summaries, or operator docs back to a stable feature reference.
.opencode/skills/sk-doc/create-feature-catalog/SKILL.md-35-
