.opencode/skills/sk-doc/create-feature-catalog/SKILL.md-173-```text
.opencode/skills/sk-doc/create-feature-catalog/SKILL.md-174-feature-catalog/
.opencode/skills/sk-doc/create-feature-catalog/SKILL.md:175:├── feature-catalog.md
.opencode/skills/sk-doc/create-feature-catalog/SKILL.md-176-├── category-name/
.opencode/skills/sk-doc/create-feature-catalog/SKILL.md-177-│   ├── feature-name.md
