.opencode/skills/sk-doc/create-feature-catalog/SKILL.md-234-## 5. ROOT CATALOG REQUIREMENTS
.opencode/skills/sk-doc/create-feature-catalog/SKILL.md-235-
.opencode/skills/sk-doc/create-feature-catalog/SKILL.md:236:The root catalog is the top-level inventory and navigation layer.
.opencode/skills/sk-doc/create-feature-catalog/SKILL.md-237-
.opencode/skills/sk-doc/create-feature-catalog/SKILL.md-238-It owns:
.opencode/skills/sk-doc/create-feature-catalog/SKILL.md-239-
.opencode/skills/sk-doc/create-feature-catalog/SKILL.md-240-- Frontmatter with title, description, trigger phrases, last updated date, and four-part version.
--
.opencode/skills/sk-doc/create-feature-catalog/SKILL.md-250-- What this feature does.
.opencode/skills/sk-doc/create-feature-catalog/SKILL.md-251-- What its current reality is.
.opencode/skills/sk-doc/create-feature-catalog/SKILL.md-252-- Where to find source-file and test detail.
.opencode/skills/sk-doc/create-feature-catalog/SKILL.md-253-
.opencode/skills/sk-doc/create-feature-catalog/SKILL.md:254:Package highlights for root catalogs:
.opencode/skills/sk-doc/create-feature-catalog/SKILL.md-255-
.opencode/skills/sk-doc/create-feature-catalog/SKILL.md-256-- Use frontmatter, including `trigger_phrases`.
.opencode/skills/sk-doc/create-feature-catalog/SKILL.md-257-- Include a short H1 intro.
.opencode/skills/sk-doc/create-feature-catalog/SKILL.md-258-- Do not include a Table of Contents.
.opencode/skills/sk-doc/create-feature-catalog/SKILL.md-259-- Do not use `<!-- ANCHOR -->` navigation comments.
.opencode/skills/sk-doc/create-feature-catalog/SKILL.md-260-- Start numbered H2 sections with `## 1. OVERVIEW`.
.opencode/skills/sk-doc/create-feature-catalog/SKILL.md-261-
.opencode/skills/sk-doc/create-feature-catalog/SKILL.md:262:Do not overload the root catalog with:
.opencode/skills/sk-doc/create-feature-catalog/SKILL.md-263-
.opencode/skills/sk-doc/create-feature-catalog/SKILL.md-264-- Exhaustive source-file tables.
.opencode/skills/sk-doc/create-feature-catalog/SKILL.md-265-- Full scenario matrices.
.opencode/skills/sk-doc/create-feature-catalog/SKILL.md-266-- Speculative future-state design.
