.opencode/skills/sk-doc/create-feature-catalog/SKILL.md-290-- A concise overview of the feature.
.opencode/skills/sk-doc/create-feature-catalog/SKILL.md-291-- A behavior-focused `HOW IT WORKS` section.
.opencode/skills/sk-doc/create-feature-catalog/SKILL.md-292-- Implementation source tables with `File | Layer | Role` columns.
