.opencode/skills/sk-doc/create-feature-catalog/SKILL.md-361-## 8. RULES
.opencode/skills/sk-doc/create-feature-catalog/SKILL.md-362-
.opencode/skills/sk-doc/create-feature-catalog/SKILL.md-363-### ✅ ALWAYS
.opencode/skills/sk-doc/create-feature-catalog/SKILL.md-364-
.opencode/skills/sk-doc/create-feature-catalog/SKILL.md:365:1. Use `assets/feature-catalog-template.md` for the root catalog scaffold.
.opencode/skills/sk-doc/create-feature-catalog/SKILL.md-366-2. Use `assets/feature-catalog-snippet-template.md` for per-feature files.
.opencode/skills/sk-doc/create-feature-catalog/SKILL.md:367:3. Preserve the canonical root path `feature-catalog/feature-catalog.md`.
.opencode/skills/sk-doc/create-feature-catalog/SKILL.md:368:4. Name category folders with a descriptive kebab-case slug such as `category-name`; let the root catalog index own display order.
.opencode/skills/sk-doc/create-feature-catalog/SKILL.md-369-5. Keep per-feature filenames stable after publication.
.opencode/skills/sk-doc/create-feature-catalog/SKILL.md-370-6. Keep per-feature filenames free of numeric prefixes.
.opencode/skills/sk-doc/create-feature-catalog/SKILL.md-371-7. Include source-file and validation anchors for every feature claim.
.opencode/skills/sk-doc/create-feature-catalog/SKILL.md-372-8. Describe current shipped behavior from the caller or operator perspective.
.opencode/skills/sk-doc/create-feature-catalog/SKILL.md:373:9. Keep the root catalog inventory-first and navigation-focused.
.opencode/skills/sk-doc/create-feature-catalog/SKILL.md-374-10. Put implementation truth in per-feature files.
.opencode/skills/sk-doc/create-feature-catalog/SKILL.md:375:11. Run shared validation on the root catalog and per-feature leaves before delivery.
.opencode/skills/sk-doc/create-feature-catalog/SKILL.md-376-12. Manually verify cross-file links, source anchors, and root-entry to feature-file parity.
.opencode/skills/sk-doc/create-feature-catalog/SKILL.md-377-13. Consume global standards and validators from `../shared/` instead of duplicating them here.
.opencode/skills/sk-doc/create-feature-catalog/SKILL.md-378-
.opencode/skills/sk-doc/create-feature-catalog/SKILL.md-379-### ⛔ NEVER
--
.opencode/skills/sk-doc/create-feature-catalog/SKILL.md-381-1. Never add a packet-local `graph-metadata.json`.
.opencode/skills/sk-doc/create-feature-catalog/SKILL.md-382-2. Never use a feature catalog as a roadmap unless future-state material is explicitly labeled.
.opencode/skills/sk-doc/create-feature-catalog/SKILL.md-383-3. Never split one feature across multiple files without a clear category boundary.
.opencode/skills/sk-doc/create-feature-catalog/SKILL.md-384-4. Never leave root entries without matching per-feature files.
.opencode/skills/sk-doc/create-feature-catalog/SKILL.md:385:5. Never leave per-feature files unlinked from the root catalog.
.opencode/skills/sk-doc/create-feature-catalog/SKILL.md-386-6. Never cite mutable packet numbers where current source paths, commands, or feature names should be used.
.opencode/skills/sk-doc/create-feature-catalog/SKILL.md-387-7. Never use numeric prefixes on per-feature filenames.
.opencode/skills/sk-doc/create-feature-catalog/SKILL.md:388:8. Never add numeric prefixes to category folder names; the root catalog index owns display order.
.opencode/skills/sk-doc/create-feature-catalog/SKILL.md-389-9. Never use underscores in category folder or per-feature filename path segments.
.opencode/skills/sk-doc/create-feature-catalog/SKILL.md-390-10. Never put manual execution scenario matrices in the catalog.
.opencode/skills/sk-doc/create-feature-catalog/SKILL.md-391-11. Never omit source anchors for feature claims.
.opencode/skills/sk-doc/create-feature-catalog/SKILL.md-392-12. Never leave long `HOW IT WORKS` sections as unbroken walls of prose.
--
.opencode/skills/sk-doc/create-feature-catalog/SKILL.md-397-1. The category taxonomy is unclear after reading the target system.
.opencode/skills/sk-doc/create-feature-catalog/SKILL.md-398-2. Source anchors cannot be found for a claimed feature.
.opencode/skills/sk-doc/create-feature-catalog/SKILL.md-399-3. The requested catalog mixes shipped behavior with planned behavior.
.opencode/skills/sk-doc/create-feature-catalog/SKILL.md-400-4. Existing docs conflict about feature names or current reality.
.opencode/skills/sk-doc/create-feature-catalog/SKILL.md:401:5. Validation fails in `../shared/scripts/validate_document.py` and the safe fix is not obvious.
.opencode/skills/sk-doc/create-feature-catalog/SKILL.md-402-6. Published category or feature slugs would need to change without a deliberate rename migration.
