.opencode/skills/sk-doc/create-feature-catalog/SKILL.md-412-| Missing source anchors | Catalog claims become hard to audit | Add implementation and validation file references in the per-feature file |
.opencode/skills/sk-doc/create-feature-catalog/SKILL.md-413-| Writing execution-heavy scenario detail in the catalog | Blurs the boundary with playbooks | Keep execution matrices in playbooks, not the catalog |
.opencode/skills/sk-doc/create-feature-catalog/SKILL.md-414-| Playbook cross-references drifting from catalog names | Inventory and validation no longer match | Update catalog and playbook links together when a feature name changes |
.opencode/skills/sk-doc/create-feature-catalog/SKILL.md-415-| Wall of prose in `HOW IT WORKS` | Long unbroken sections lose scannability and navigation anchors | Add H3 subheadings whenever the section exceeds three paragraphs |
.opencode/skills/sk-doc/create-feature-catalog/SKILL.md:416:| Missing `trigger_phrases` in frontmatter | Feature is invisible to doc-trigger routing | Add at least three trigger phrases matching the H3 heading in the root catalog |
