.opencode/skills/sk-doc/create-manual-testing-playbook/references/common-pitfalls.md-29-## 2. COMMON PITFALLS
.opencode/skills/sk-doc/create-manual-testing-playbook/references/common-pitfalls.md-30-
.opencode/skills/sk-doc/create-manual-testing-playbook/references/common-pitfalls.md-31-| Mistake | Why It Breaks | Correct Fix |
.opencode/skills/sk-doc/create-manual-testing-playbook/references/common-pitfalls.md-32-|---|---|---|
.opencode/skills/sk-doc/create-manual-testing-playbook/references/common-pitfalls.md:33:| Keeping separate canonical `review_protocol.md` or `subagent_utilization_ledger.md` files | Splits package truth across sidecar docs | Fold shared review/orchestration rules into the root playbook |
