.opencode/skills/sk-doc/create-feature-catalog/references/examples.md:48:The catalog groups a large MCP surface into category folders, each holding one file per feature. The root `feature-catalog.md` is the only navigation surface and owns the section order; the folder names do not encode ordering. Both the category folders and the per-feature files use bare descriptive kebab-case slugs with no numeric prefix.
