.opencode/specs/sk-doc/019-sk-doc-router-alignment/020-router-unification-program/007-unified-refactor-implementation/013-create-skill-alignment/spec.md:150:- **SC-004**: A mint or freshness failure cannot be mistaken for compiled-ready output.
