.opencode/specs/sk-doc/019-sk-doc-router-alignment/020-router-unification-program/007-unified-refactor-implementation/012-default-on-decision/spec.md-164-|------|------|--------|------------|
.opencode/specs/sk-doc/019-sk-doc-router-alignment/020-router-unification-program/007-unified-refactor-implementation/012-default-on-decision/spec.md-165-| Risk | Premise capture — treating default-on as a switch | Flips an undocumented flag that inverts the kill-switch for zero routing benefit | This decision reframes default-on as a P4 outcome gated on P0–P3; the flip is never this phase's action |
.opencode/specs/sk-doc/019-sk-doc-router-alignment/020-router-unification-program/007-unified-refactor-implementation/012-default-on-decision/spec.md:166:| Risk | Silent drift normalized as "compiled" | A drifted hub serves legacy while dashboards claim compiled | P1 drift-CI fails re-mint-required; P0 observability distinguishes drifted from broken |
.opencode/specs/sk-doc/019-sk-doc-router-alignment/020-router-unification-program/007-unified-refactor-implementation/012-default-on-decision/spec.md-167-| Risk | Duplicated allowlist diverges | `COMPILED_ROUTING_HUBS` and `HUB_CHILD` drift apart, mis-gating hubs | P3 single-sources eligibility to "valid fresh manifest exists"; both predicates derive from it |
.opencode/specs/sk-doc/019-sk-doc-router-alignment/020-router-unification-program/007-unified-refactor-implementation/012-default-on-decision/spec.md:168:| Risk | Runtime resolver coupled to a spec-tree path | A spec renumber breaks all compiled routing to the sentinel | REQ-005 P0 remediation: promote the resolver to a stable runtime path or document the coupling as a named drift source with a guard |
.opencode/specs/sk-doc/019-sk-doc-router-alignment/020-router-unification-program/007-unified-refactor-implementation/012-default-on-decision/spec.md:169:| Dependency | Frozen benchmark scorer (three pinned files) | Any edit invalidates the parity baseline the whole program rests on | Restated as a hard pin per migration step; never edited |
.opencode/specs/sk-doc/019-sk-doc-router-alignment/020-router-unification-program/007-unified-refactor-implementation/012-default-on-decision/spec.md:170:| Dependency | Sibling `013`/`014` alignment phases | Onboarding (create-skill) and validation (benchmarks) must consume this phase's contracts | REQ-007 cross-links; the contracts live here once and are referenced, not restated |
.opencode/specs/sk-doc/019-sk-doc-router-alignment/020-router-unification-program/007-unified-refactor-implementation/012-default-on-decision/spec.md-171-
.opencode/specs/sk-doc/019-sk-doc-router-alignment/020-router-unification-program/007-unified-refactor-implementation/012-default-on-decision/spec.md-172-<!-- /ANCHOR:risks -->
